OL,3,CDecision on plans for Europe's biggest
OL,4,Csolar farm delayed until September
OL,6,FA decision on plans to create what
OL,7,Fwould be Europe's biggest solar farm
OL,8,Fin Oxfordshire has been delayed until
OL,9,FSeptember, the Government has
OL,10,Fconfirmed.
OL,12,FBotley West Solar Farm would cover
OL,13,Fmore than 3000 acres north and west of
OL,14,FOxford.
OL,16,FPhotovolt Development Partners - the
OL,17,Fcompany behind the scheme say it would
OL,18,Fprovide enough energy for around
OL,19,F330,000 homes.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
