CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774598700
OL,3,CDecision on plans for Europe's biggest
OL,4,Csolar farm delayed until September
OL,6,FBut those against it say it would
OL,7,Fimpact the countryside and the site
OL,8,Fshould be smaller.
OL,10,FThe Department for Energy Security and
OL,11,FNet Zero wants to collect information
OL,12,Fbefore refusing or granting the plan.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
