CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774598700
OL,3,CDecision on plans for Europe's biggest
OL,4,Csolar farm delayed until September
OL,6,FIn a statement, Martin McCluskey,
OL,7,FMinister for Energy Consumers said:
OL,8,F"This Statement concerns an
OL,9,Fapplication for development consent
OL,10,Fmade under the Planning Act 2008 by
OL,11,FPhotovolt Development Partners (PVDP)
OL,12,Fon behalf of SolarFive Ltd for the
OL,13,Fconstruction and operation of a solar
OL,14,Ffarm on land in West Oxfordshire,
OL,15,FCherwell and Vale of White Horse
OL,16,FDistricts, across approximately 1,400
OL,17,Fhectares.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774598700
OL,3,CDecision on plans for Europe's biggest
OL,4,Csolar farm delayed until September
OL,6,F"Under section 107(1) of the Planning
OL,7,FAct 2008, the Secretary of State must
OL,8,Fmake a decision on an application
OL,9,Fwithin three months of the receipt of
OL,10,Fthe Examining Authority's report
OL,11,Funless a new deadline is set using the
OL,12,Fpower under section 107(3) of the
OL,13,FPlanning Act 2008.
OL,15,F"Where a new deadline is set, the
OL,16,FSecretary of State must make a
OL,17,FStatement to Parliament to announce it.
OL,19,F"The current statutory deadline for
OL,20,Fthe decision on the Botley West Solar
OL,21,FFarm application is 10 May 2026.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774598700
OL,3,CDecision on plans for Europe's biggest
OL,4,Csolar farm delayed until September
OL,6,F"I have decided to set a new deadline
OL,7,Fof no later than 10 September 2026 for
OL,8,Fdeciding this application.
OL,10,F"This is to enable my Department to
OL,11,Fseek further information from the
OL,12,Fapplicant with sufficient time to
OL,13,Fallow for consideration of this
OL,14,Finformation by other interested
OL,15,Fparties.
OL,17,F"The decision to set the new deadline
OL,18,Ffor this application is without
OL,19,Fprejudice to the decision on whether
OL,20,Fto grant or refuse development
OL,21,Fconsent."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
